'I have to take it on the chin. I am frustrated and disappointed that I am not on the plane (to Australia and New Zealand).

'It's gutting, it's frustrating not to be going there, especially when you have put so much in.

'But that's the way of the world. I have to get over it. I wish all the guys all of the best.'

